R

rechecking(String) - Method in class org.jetbrains.jetCheck.PropertyChecker.Parameters
Deprecated.
To catch your attention. It's fine to call this method during test debugging, but it should not be committed to version control and used in regression tests, because any changes in the test itself or the framework can render the passed argument obsolete. For regression testing, it's recommended to code the failing scenario explicitly.
